            <ol>
              <li><p>Along <m>y=mx</m>, the limit is:
                  <md>
                    <mrow>\lim_{(x,y)\to(0,0)} \frac{\sin(x^2)}{y} \amp  =  \lim_{x\to 0} \frac{\sin(x^2)}{mx}</mrow>
                    <intertext>apply L'H\^opital's Rule</intertext>
